@mikewalch and I were discussing how avoid api module depending on core.   Uncertain about specifics w/ properties, but could have one entry point for the API like the following.    This entry point could use reflection to avoid depending on core module.

``` java
class FluoFactory {

   FluoFactory(Properties props){

   }

   LoaderExecutor newLoaderExecutor(){
        String clazz = props.get("io.fluo.loaderExecutor.class", "core.LoaderExecutor")
        //instanstiate clazz via reflection and return
   }

   Snapshot newSnapshot(){
   }

   FluoAdmin newFluoAdmin(){
   }
}
```

We also discussed possibility of moving map reduce to its own module.
